===声调===
特里基语所有方言都有声调。科帕拉特里基语的声调系统的记载最为完善，有8种声调。<ref name="ReferenceA">Hollenbach, Barbara. The Phonology and Morphology of Tone and Laryngeals in Copala Trique. Ph.D Thesis, University of Arizona. 1984</ref>

特里基语的声调一般用五度标记法记录调值。<ref name="ReferenceA"/>

特里基语中，科帕拉方言经历了最多的元音消变，大量的非词尾音节失去了它们的元音。与其他欧托-曼格语系语言类似，最终形成了大量复辅音。例如Itunyoso方言的si<sup>5</sup>kuj<sup>5</sup>“牛”对应科帕拉方言的skuj<sup>5</sup>。

其他方言的声调系统比科帕拉方言还要复杂。Itunyoso方言有9种声调，<ref name=":0">DiCanio, Christian. [http://www.acsu.buffalo.edu/~cdicanio/pdfs/DiCanio_dissertation_papersaver.pdf The Phonetics and Phonology of San Martín Itunyoso Trique] {{Wayback|url=http://www.acsu.buffalo.edu/~cdicanio/pdfs/DiCanio_dissertation_papersaver.pdf |date=20211128104905 }}. Ph.D Thesis, University of California, Berkeley. 2008.</ref>Chicahuaxtla特里基语至少有10种声调，<ref>Good, Claude. Diccionario Triqui, volume 20 of Serie de Vocabularios Indigenas. Summer Institute of Linguistics, Mexico. 1979.</ref>较多的分析可以有16种。<ref>Longacre, Robert E. Proto-Mixtecan. In Indiana University Research Center in Anthropology, Folklore, and Linguistics, volume 5. Indiana University Research Center in Anthropology, Folklore, and Linguistics, Bloomington. 1957</ref>

